videos.description: Christyn Williams fires a quick pass to Anna Makurat who pulls up for a smooth 3-pointer in the first quarter for UConn.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Makurat pulls up for 3 from the top of the arc) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Makurat pulls up for 3 from the top of the arc

videos.description: Aubrey Griffin impresses on defense, denying Tulane and sending the ball the other way for a Megan Walker 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UConn turns defense into offense off Griffin's block) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: UConn turns defense into offense off Griffin's block

videos.description: Olivia Nelson-Ododa is the beneficiary of Connecticut's smooth ball movement around the arc.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Huskies' skillful ball movement sets up Nelson-Ododa's layup) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Huskies' skillful ball movement sets up Nelson-Ododa's layup

videos.description: Anna Makurat shows patience before sending a slick bounce pass over to Megan Walker in the paint, who then takes it to the hoop, fakes out her Tulane defender and lays it in late in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Walker fakes and lays it in for UConn) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Walker fakes and lays it in for UConn

videos.description: Connecticut's Anna Makurat steals the ball away from Tulane on the defensive end, races down court and drains a tough layup while drawing contact.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Makurat steals, converts and-1 in transition) 2020/2/19

videos.headline: Makurat steals, converts and-1 in transition
